performs the previous bit-slice accelerator, Bit-fusion, over $\\times3.65$\nhigher area-efficiency, $\\times3.88$ higher energy-efficiency, and $\\times5.35$\nhigher throughput.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 06:49:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-16"}
