hardness result\nthat there exists no polynomial algorithm whose output $S$ satisfies\n$f(S)+\\ell(S)\\geq0.478\\cdot f(OPT)+\\ell(OPT)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 07:59:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2022 07:46:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-13"}
